13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Foiz kalkulyatori barcha asosiy amallarni bajaradi: sondan foizni topish, bir son ikkinchisidan necha foizligini aniqlash, foizni qo'shish yoki ayirish, foiz o'zgarishini hisoblash. Bu O'zbekistonda kundalik hisob-kitoblar, biznes, savdo va ta'lim uchun universal vosita."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Asosiy formulalar: A sondan X% = A × X / 100. A soni B sondan (A / B × 100)% ni tashkil etadi. A soniga X% qo'shish = A × (1 + X/100). A sondan X% ayirish = A × (1 − X/100). Foiz o'zgarishi = (Yangi − Eski) / Eski × 100%. Barcha formulalar o'zbek so'midagi har qanday summalar bilan ishlaydi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekiston uchun amaliy misollar: 10 000 000 so'mdan 12% "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/qqs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"QQS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" = 1 200 000 so'm. 8 000 000 ish haqidan 12% JShDS = 960 000 so'm. 500 000 s